<DOCNO> XIE19990101.0016 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-01 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Tunis Stock Exchange Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TUNIS, December 31 (Xinhua) -- The Tunis Stock Exchange index
closed at 464.56 points Thursday, up 0.16 percent from
Wednesday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A daily bulletin of the bourse said 748,159 shares changed
hands in 228 deals, and the turnover was 18,227,887 dinars
(15,850,336 U.S. dollars). 
</P>
