<HEADLINE> Presidents of Ecuador, Peru to Meet </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
QUITO, December 31 (Xinhua) -- Ecuador's President Jamil
Mahuad is to meet his Peruvian counterpart Alberto Fujimori again
next Monday in Brasilia, capital of Brazil, Ecuadorian Vice
Foreign Minister Diego Ribadeneira said on Thursday.
</P>
