<HEADLINE> Euro to Favor Spain Stock Market </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MADRID, December 31 (Xinhua) -- The implementation of a single
currency, the euro, in part of Europe will be good for the stock
market as it will increase liquidity and the volume of trade, the
president of the Madrid Stock Market Antonio Zoido said here on
Thursday.
</P>
<P>
